document.full_text: world leaders warned of revenge attacks after osama bin laden was killed in a u.s. assault in pakistan on monday that brought to a dramatic end the long manhunt for the al qaeda leader who had become the most powerful symbol of islamist militancy.
document.title: fears of qaeda vengeance after u.s. kills osama
